dc_description_s: The linework shown in this layer was originally obtained from Street Centerlines data set in the mid-1990's.  It has since been maintained seperately by the Planning Dept. As a result some roads may no longer spatially register with the street centerline base data. Arterial_circ contains an attribute, ART_DESIG, that defines 7 classes of arterials, including planned roads that do not yet exist.  A similar data set, MajorRoads, contains existing roadways only.
